snippet.title: Ultra Kaiju Monster Rancher - 1st Trailer
snippet.description:
Raise your very own Ultra Kaiju in Ultra Kaiju Monster Rancher! Feed them, assign them training drills and do so much more with your Kaiju!

Get ready for some time at the ranch when Ultra Kaiju Monster Rancher comes to you on the Nintendo Switch™ in 2022. 

#UltraKaijuMonsterRancher #BandaiNamco
